    • init

      public void init(ProfileViewModel profileViewModel, ViewHandler viewHandler)
      Init method, sets profile view model instance and view handler instance. Also initializes the top panel, the bottom panel view and the binding of the text fields and labels with the profile view model.
      Parameters:
      profileViewModel - the profile view model instance
      viewHandler - the view handler instance

    • handleButtonCancelClicked

      private void handleButtonCancelClicked(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
      This method is called when the cancel button in the profile view is clicked. It triggers the redirect to the start view.
      Parameters:
      event - action event

    • handleButtonSaveClicked

      private void handleButtonSaveClicked(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
      This method is called when the save button in the profile view is clicked. It triggers the save of the profile data and redirects to the start view, if the save was successful.
      Parameters:
      event - action event
